	<abstract encodinganalog="520$a" label="Abstract:">The Baruj Salinas papers measure 0.4 linear feet and date from 1971-1996.  The collection documents the artist's prolific painting career and his friendships and professional relationships with a variety of contemporary artist in the U.S. and Europe. The papers of Baruj Salinas are an important addition to the documentation of Cuban-American art and artists.</abstract>

	<langmaterial>The records are in <language>English</language> and <language>Spanish</language>.
